Package: TweetLocViz
Type: Package
Title: Twitter Topic Modeling and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andreas Buchmueller, ...
Maintainer: Andreas Buchmueller <a.buchmueller@stud.uni-goettingen.de>
Description: TweetLocVis enables users to sample geo-located twitter data
    with a regular twitter account. Additionally it comes with abilities for automated
    pre-processing of tweets for a variety of topic models such as LDA and NMF as well as 
    visualizaion capabilities enabling the user a board-range of methods for analysis
    and monitoring the public discourse.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/abuchmueller/TweetLocViz
